<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Nicolas </PERSON> <PERSON> B. </PERSON> <PERSON> Tatro </PERSON> is chief of bureau in <LOCATION> Israel </LOCATION> for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>.
