ter to the <ORGANIZATION> Justice </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Department </ORGANIZATION>'s internal investigations office. <PERSON> Cranston </PERSON>, D-Calif., is one of five senators who intervened on <PERSON> Keating </PERSON>'s behalf with federal regulators The <ORGANIZATION> FBI </ORGANIZATION> is investigating whether whether <PERSON> Cranston </PERSON> and the other senators violated any laws by taking campaign donations from <PERSON> Keating </PERSON> and lobbying federal regulators.
