 Here are the pronunciations of the names of leading figures in <LOCATION> Chile </LOCATION>'s presidential election: <PERSON> AUGUSTO </PERSON> <PERSON> PINOCHET </PERSON> _ ow-GOOSE-toh peen-oh-CHET. <PERSON> PATRICIO </PERSON> <PERSON> AYLWIN </PERSON> _ pah-TREE-shee-oh AISLE-ween. <PERSON> HERNAN </PERSON> <PERSON> BUCHI </PERSON> _ ehr-NAHN BEE-chee. <PERSON> FRANCISCO </PERSON> <PERSON> ERRAZURIZ </PERSON> _ frahn-SEES-koh eh-RAS-oo-ris.
