<HEAD>The Fascinating and the Not-So: Another Decade-Full of Trivia</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By SCOTT WILLIAMS</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
 What do you remember about the'80s?
</TEXT>
