<HEAD>MeraBank To Get $450 Million Capital Infusion from Pinnacle West</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By MEL REISNER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>PHOENIX (AP) </DATELINE>
